    ORDER BY [b].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN (

) AS [t0] ON [t].[AuthorId] = [t0].[Id]
